title: One Lucky Duck
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, American, Juice bar, Take-out, All Raw
description: Originated from NYC, this is a juice bar and raw food cafe that's all vegan except for honey in a few items. Offers pressed juices, shakes, salads, and raw meals. Also sells vegan cookies and macaroons, granola, and nut bars and juice cleansing programs. Uses eco-friendly packaging. Casual, has Wi-Fi.
